            "content_html": "\n  <p>\n    这里展示的是我日常练习和在项目中的设计作品，包括的内容有界面设计、插画设计、动效设计、3D 设计等等。\n  </p>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper gallery-wrapper--wide\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"3\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/0f13384a3279aa5f0d8def24f61e4d9c.webp\" data-size=\"800x600\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/0f13384a3279aa5f0d8def24f61e4d9c.webp\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/2f3bfa6a8cb81f466550c6a4a348af65.webp\" data-size=\"800x600\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/2f3bfa6a8cb81f466550c6a4a348af65.webp\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/5d52f5ec779322e052ca4781e8b7f601.gif\" data-size=\"800x600\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/5d52f5ec779322e052ca4781e8b7f601.gif\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/6d39d3c34ef384a5301e4d78b5729cc9.gif\" data-size=\"800x600\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/6d39d3c34ef384a5301e4d78b5729cc9.gif\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/7a82d20995a6f7ed4e90aa0ad8e559ca.webp\" data-size=\"800x600\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://franllk.github.io/media/posts/8/gallery/7a82d20995a6f7ed4e90aa0ad8e559ca.webp\" height=\"600\" width=\"800\" alt=\"\" />\n      </a>\n   